text:
It seems that the class org.apache.poi.ss.usermodel.WorkbookFactory
is missing from the archive poi-bin-3.6-20091214.tar.gz.

creator: apache@gagravarr.org
text: Make sure you have all the poi jars on the classpath. The xssf / xslf / xwpf classes are in the ooxml jar.
